---
categories:
  - Spring
date:
  - 2022-11-28 14:35:05
---

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">后端数据传递到前端接界面时，有时实体类不可避免的会存在相同的属性，传递到前端界面无法区分</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#111111">&nbsp;</span></span></span>
</p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">为了解决这个问题，可以在</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">Controller</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">的方法中用</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">@ModelAttribute</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">()</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">注解给两个实体类上添加别名，</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">然后在</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">@ControllerAdvice</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">注解的类方法中使用</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">@InitBinder</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#111111">注解，为添加了别名的实体类的参数全部添加上前缀或后缀等操作来区分</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#111111">&nbsp;</span></span></span>
</p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">我有两个实体类，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Book </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Author</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">class</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">Book</span><span style="color:black">{<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
                style="color:blue">private</span> <span style="color:black">String name;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            </span><span style="color:blue">private</span> <span style="color:black">Long price;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            </span><span style="color:green">//getter/setter</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">}</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><br><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">public</span> <span
                style="color:blue">class</span> <span style="color:#a31515">Author</span><span
                style="color:black">{<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color:blue">private</span> <span
                style="color:black">String name;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color:blue">private</span>
            <span style="color:black">Integer age;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
                style="color:green">//getter/setter</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">}</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">此时，如果我定义一个数据添加接口，如下：</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@PostMapping</span>("/book")</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">void</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">addBook</span><span style="color:black">(Book book, Author
                author){<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; System.out.println(book);<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                System.out.println(author);<br>}</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这个时候，添加操作就会有问题，因为两个实体类都有一个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> name </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性，从前端传递时
                ，无法区分。此时，通过</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> @ControllerAdvice </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的全局数据预处理可以解决这个问题</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47"><strong>示例</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="color:#e67e22;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">bookController.java</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@Controller</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">class</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">book</span><span style="color:#a31515">Controller</span><span
                style="color:black">{</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#70ad47"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">//</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">给接口中的变量取别名</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@PostMapping</span>("/book")</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">void</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">addBook</span><span style="color:black">(</span><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ModelAttribute</span>("b")Book book, <span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ModelAttribute</span>("a")Author author){<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            System.out.println(book);<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; System.out.println(author);<br>}</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">}</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ed7d31">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="color:#e67e22;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">InitBinder</span></span><span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Handler</span></span><span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">.java</span></span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ControllerAdvice</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">class</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">MyGlobalExceptionHandler</span><span style="color:black">{</span></span></span>
</p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#70ad47"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">//</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> @ControllerAdvice </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标记的类中添加</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">@InitBinder</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@InitBinder</span>("b")</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">void</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">b</span><span style="color:black">(WebDataBinder binder){</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; binder.setFieldDefaultPrefix(</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#a31515">"b."</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">);</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#70ad47"> //</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#70ad47">绑定前缀</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">}</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#2b91af">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@InitBinder</span>("a")</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span> <span style="color:blue">void</span> <span
                style="color:#a31515">a</span><span style="color:black">(WebDataBinder binder){</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; binder.setFieldDefaultPrefix(</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#a31515">"a."</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black">);</span></span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#70ad47">//</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#70ad47">绑定前缀</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">}</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">}</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ed7d31">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">@InitBinder("b")
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">注解表示该方法用来处理和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Book</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和相关的参数</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在方法中</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">给参数添加一个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> b </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">前缀</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">即请求参数要有</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">b</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">前缀</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#111111">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">请求发送时</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">通过给不同对象的参数添加不同的前缀</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">可以实现参数的区分</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">.</span></span></li>
</ul>
